# Git Fork Safety

This repository is a fork of `grafana/grafana`. All work targets `ChrisatCursor/grafana` only.

## Before Any PR Creation

Run this command before creating your first pull request in a session:

```bash
gh repo set-default ChrisatCursor/grafana
```

This prevents `gh pr create` from defaulting to the upstream `grafana/grafana`.

## Rules

- **Push**: Only push to `origin` (which must be `ChrisatCursor/grafana`)
- **PRs**: All PRs target `ChrisatCursor/grafana`. Always use `--repo ChrisatCursor/grafana` as a safety flag if unsure.
- **Never**: Do not push to or create PRs against `grafana/grafana` unless explicitly instructed by the user.
- **Verify**: If uncertain, run `git remote -v` and `gh repo set-default --view` to confirm before pushing or creating PRs.
